CopperLP Reproducibility Package

Status: Development snapshot
Version: 0.1.0
Last updated: 2026-07-23

This repository currently contains the five SageMath experiment scripts
and the batch runner.

Experiment parameters are configured manually in the configuration section
at the beginning of each SageMath script.

The files under profiles/, instances/, and logs/ are currently templates or
placeholders. They are not automatically loaded or populated by the current
experiment scripts.

A numbered reproducibility release will be prepared after the exact Table 2
parameter profiles, fixed test instances, and verified reference results have
been added.
